 class=\"mtk1\">=</span><span class=\"mtk4\">{</span><span class=\"mtk12\">item</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk12\">url</span><span class=\"mtk4\">}</span><span class=\"mtk17\">&gt;</span><span class=\"mtk4\">{</span><span class=\"mtk12\">item</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk12\">title</span><span class=\"mtk4\">}</span><span class=\"mtk17\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk4\">a</span><span class=\"mtk17\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\"># start-insert</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk17\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk10\">StyledColumn</span><span class=\"mtk17\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk17\">&lt;</span><span class=\"mtk10\">StyledColumn</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">width</span><span class=\"mtk1\">=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;30%&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk17\">&gt;</span><span class=\"mtk4\">{</span><span class=\"mtk12\">item</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk12\">author</span><span class=\"mtk4\">}</span><span class=\"mtk17\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk10\">StyledColumn</span><span class=\"mtk17\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk17\">&lt;</span><span class=\"mtk10\">StyledColumn</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">width</span><span class=\"mtk1\">=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;10%&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk17\">&gt;</span><span class=\"mtk4\">{</span><span class=\"mtk12\">item</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk12\">num_comments</span><span class=\"mtk4\">}</span><span class=\"mtk17\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk10\">StyledColumn</span><span class=\"mtk17\">&g